# Title
;The best of the Web
Okuyingcwenga kuWebhu


;Firefox changed browsing forever by putting users first and offering a new level of choice and innovation online. Now we’re doing it all over again with Firefox OS, while bringing the same superior browsing experience to your smartphone. So you can take control of your life online and get the best the Web has to offer no matter where you go.
I-Firefox ishintshe indlela yokubrawuza ngokuba ibeke phambili abasebenzisi iphinde ihlinzeke ngokungakhethwa kukho okusha kanye nobuciko be-inthanethi. Manje sesiyaphind afuthi nge-Firefox OS, njengoba sikulethela ukubrawuza okuseqophelweni elifanayo ku-smartphone yakho. Ukuze ukwazi ukulawula impilo yakho ku-inthanethi uthole okungcono kakhulu okuhlinzekwa yiWebhu.


